### Test Basic Authentication

@hostname = https://localhost:7142

### Test public endpoint (no auth required)
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/public

### Test endpoint that accepts both JWT and Basic auth - Using Basic Auth
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/both
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM=

### Test endpoint that accepts both JWT and Basic auth - Using Basic Auth (user credentials)
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/both
Authorization: Basic dXNlcjp1c2VyMTIz

### Test Basic-only endpoint
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/basic
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM=

### Test Basic-only endpoint with user credentials
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/basic
Authorization: Basic dXNlcjp1c2VyMTIz

### Test JWT-only endpoint with Basic Auth (should fail)
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/jwt
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM=

### Test with invalid credentials (should fail)
GET {{hostname}}/api/secure/basic
Authorization: Basic aW52YWxpZDppbnZhbGlk

### WeatherForecast with Basic Authentication
GET {{hostname}}/weatherforecast
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM=

###
# Note: Credentials encoded in Base64:
# YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQxMjM= = admin:password123
# dXNlcjp1c2VyMTIz = user:user123
# aW52YWxpZDppbnZhbGlk = invalid:invalid
